---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">

  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-sm">

    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      This website does not collect personal information unless you choose to provide it (such as contacting us via email).
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Local Storage</h2>

    <p>
      This site may use your browser’s local storage to save preferences such as reflections, bookmarks, or progress. This data stays on your device and is not transmitted to any server.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Third-Party Services</h2>

    <p>
      In the future, this website may use third-party services such as analytics or advertisements. These services may use cookies or similar technologies.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-medium">Changes</h2>

    <p>
      This policy may be updated from time to time.
    </p>

  </div>

</BaseLayout>